description:

Special features        The 24K Gold Dust provides a tightening
effect for the face and neckline whilst aiding the
intense nutrition and revitalization obtained from
the MINERALS at the same time.
Kit Contents & How to Use        STEP 1 Mix the ratio of gel and powder into a suitable bowl.
STEP 2 Using a spatula, preferably plastic, stir both phases together briskly for about 30 
seconds, forming a smooth paste.
STEP 3 With the same spatula apply and extend the mask on the face within about 4 minutes,
before it starts to set. It is possible to cover eyes and lips.
STEP 4 Leave the mask on to act for 15 to 20 minutes.
STEP 5 Remove the mask in one piece.
